    "One study found positive effects throughout (Park et al., 2018), one found null effects (Ray et al., 2021) and three others found mixed effects depending on other factors such as AI accuracy or saliency map quality (Alipour et al., 2020; Lerman et al., 2021; Ray et al., 2019).",
    "Thus, even when the task requires participants to understand the role of particular image features, this is no guarantee that saliency maps will be useful.",
